$ Oracle: V$VERSION
@ v$version

code {
select
   banner,
   banner_full,
   regexp_replace(banner_full, '.*\n(.*)', '\1') banner_full_2nd_line,
   banner_legacy,
   con_id
from
   v$version;
code }

sa:

  The view `PRODUCT_COMPONENT_VERSION` selects from `v$version`.

